    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长维勒鲁瓦表示绿色量化宽松既不可取，也不可能</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ecb-s-villeroy-says-green-qe-neither-desirable-nor-possible</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员弗朗索瓦·维勒鲁瓦·德加豪表示，欧洲央行无法解决绿色转型的融资挑战，因为这在法律上是不可能的，而且可能会引发通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ecb-s-villeroy-says-green-qe-neither-desirable-nor-possible</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 15:55:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Alantra因投资银行业务低迷而裁员德国员工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/alantra-cuts-germany-staff-in-half-amid-investment-banking-slump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Alantra Partners SA 已将其德国子公司的员工人数削减了约一半，这家西班牙公司在交易枯竭后重组了其投资银行业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/alantra-cuts-germany-staff-in-half-amid-investment-banking-slump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:02:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于石化和税收支出疲弱，Reliance 未达到利润预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ambani-s-reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-petrochemicals-drag</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁穆克什·安巴尼(Mukesh Ambani)领导的信实工业有限公司(Reliance Industries Ltd.)公布的季度利润低于预期，原因是石化业务持续疲软，税收增加抵消了消费部门的增长和其他收入的大幅增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/ambani-s-reliance-misses-profit-estimate-on-petrochemicals-drag</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 13:40:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着盈利的增加，股市停止了 2 万亿美元的暴跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/asian-traders-brace-for-key-data-us-futures-rise-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[股市在遭遇 2 万亿美元的抛售后出现反弹，美国企业迎来第一季度财报最为繁忙的一周，这将是决定股市前景的关键。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/asian-traders-brace-for-key-data-us-futures-rise-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 22:28:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>智利新关税使炼钢业再次盈利，上限跃升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/chile-slaps-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-to-bolster-local-industry</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在当局对部分中国钢铁产品征收关税后，智利钢铁和铁矿石生产商Cap SA股价创下两周来最大涨幅，此举促使该公司推翻了关闭工厂的决定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-21/chile-slaps-tariffs-on-chinese-steel-to-bolster-local-industry</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 21 Apr 2024 18:11:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>詹纳斯·亨德森表示，实际收益率“非常有吸引力”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/real-yields-are-very-attractive-says-janus-kerschner-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Janus Henderson Investors美国证券化产品主管兼投资组合经理John Kerschner表示，不要考虑日常波动，实际收益率非常有吸引力。他与索纳利·巴萨克就“彭博真实收益率”进行了交谈。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-19/real-yields-are-very-attractive-says-janus-kerschner-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 19:52:12 GMT</pubDate>
